00:20:40,791 --> 00:20:42,125
Whaddayasay?

506
00:20:42,208 --> 00:20:43,791
You wanna maybe be my friend?

507
00:20:43,875 --> 00:20:44,583
Huh?

508
00:20:44,666 --> 00:20:46,000
What did you say?

509
00:20:46,083 --> 00:20:47,250
[KODAKA]
"What did you say" my ass.

510
00:20:47,333 --> 00:20:48,916
Don't be stupid.

511
00:20:51,000 --> 00:20:55,208
[RIKA] Yeah, well, don't be
stupid yourself, stupid.

512
00:20:55,291 --> 00:20:57,541
I'm already your friend, right?

513
00:20:57,625 --> 00:20:59,916
We all already are your friends.

514
00:21:00,000 --> 00:21:03,791
[KODAKA laughing]

515
00:21:03,875 --> 00:21:05,500
[KODAKA]
It was then I realized,

516
00:21:05,583 --> 00:21:08,750
ten years ago had
happened all over again.

517
00:21:08,833 --> 00:21:10,375
You're wrong.

518
00:21:10,458 --> 00:21:12,416
I'll prove I'm not weak!

519
00:21:14,916 --> 00:21:17,666
[KODAKA] Except this time,
Sora's not here.

520
00:21:17,750 --> 00:21:20,375
Neither is proud little
Taka for that matter.

521
00:21:22,375 --> 00:21:25,958
It's just weak,
pathetic, probably fractured,

522
00:21:26,041 --> 00:21:28,500
Kodaka Hasegawa.

523
00:21:28,583 --> 00:21:30,875
Rika, will you help me, please?

524
00:21:30,958 --> 00:21:32,625
[RIKA]
Sure thing.

525
00:21:34,666 --> 00:21:36,250
[KODAKA] Well, this is one
for the Neighbors Club

526
00:21:36,333 --> 00:21:37,625
History Books.

527
00:21:37,708 --> 00:21:39,583
We made friends.

528
00:21:50,583 --> 00:21:52,166
Hey, Sena.

529
00:21:55,458 --> 00:21:58,583
I wanted to-- Well, I--

530
00:21:58,666 --> 00:21:59,583
[PHONE]
You've got mail.

531
00:22:00,458 --> 00:22:01,541
[PHONE]
You've got mail.

532
00:22:05,125 --> 00:22:06,500
[YOZORA]
I'm leaving on a journey.

533
00:22:06,583 --> 00:22:08,541
Please don't come
looking for me.

534
00:22:10,666 --> 00:22:12,083
[EVERYONE screaming]
What?

535
00:22:17,916 --> 00:22:18,916
[KODAKA]
Of course.

536
00:22:19,000 --> 00:22:20,875
I don't know what
I was thinking.

537
00:22:20,958 --> 00:22:24,458
Looks like our tragically flawed
youth isn't over just yet.

